videos.description: California's Ivan Rabb gets a block on defense and Jabari Bird throws down an alley-oop in transition.
videos.headline: Cal gets a huge block at one end and follows it up with an alley-oop

videos.description: Jabari Bird lays in a transition alley-oop after being fouled
videos.headline: Jabari Bird lays in a transition alley-oop after being fouled

videos.description: Arizona's Kobi Simmons flys to the rim for a one-handed dunk against Cal.
videos.headline: Simmons throws down a monster one-handed dunk in Arizona's win

videos.description: California's Kingsley Okoroh finds Jabari Bird open for a two-handed dunk
videos.headline: Cal's Jabari Bird slams home a two-handed dunk

videos.description: Arizona's Rawle Alkins makes an and-1 layup with under three minutes to go against California.
videos.headline: Alkins' make and-1 bucket to pushes Arizona's lead to 6

videos.description: California's Jabari Bird drains a 3-Pointer off an inbounds pass, follows it up with the steal, but fails to connect on a second three.
videos.headline: Cal's Jabari Bird comes up short of two straight 3-Pointers

videos.description: Postgame Breakdown of Arizona's 67-62 victory over California
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown of Arizona's 67-62 victory over California
